title: Kvadrat Salat
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, European
description: Busy vegetarian salad bar located in the Kvadraturen district close to the shopping street Karl Johan. The salad bar includes legumes, greens, fruit, bread (some with dairy and/or egg, and more. Has juices. Seemed to have taken over the location of the now defunct Prince Lunchbar.
